2017 First Half Results

                    Wednesday, 26th July after the close of the Paris market  











Chairman’s message



“In 2016, amid economic and geopolitical uncertainties, our Group delivered record results. The creativity of our Maisons, the quest for excellence that inspires them, and their entrepreneurial spirit are the keys to our success.” 


Bernard Arnault, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer

Read more









Key figures


134,000 employees                
37.6 billion euros revenue in 2016                
19%  operating margin in 2016                





Activities




 


 

                        LVMH has a unique portfolio of prestigious brands in five different sectors: Wines & Spirits, Fashion & Leather Goods, Perfumes & Cosmetics, Watches & Jewelry, Selective retailing and Other activities.                    



 











