Your career at LVMH




Recruitment

                                    To support the growth of our Group, we strive to attract and develop the most talented people around the world. External recruitment is an essential source of fresh energy for the Group, and therefore it is a strategic pillar in our human resources policies. 





Development

                                    Building strong, creative and passionate teams and developing their skills through ambitious training is a key priority which encompasses career management, internal mobility, training, programs for high-potential managers and a proactive corporate social responsibility policy. 








                                    View our job offers 


                                    Follow us on LinkedIn 








