LVMH Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton SE: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















lvmh moet hennessy louis vuitton se
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Apparel & Textile Products
Sub-Industry: Apparel, Footwear & Acc Design
LVMH Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton SE is a diversified luxury goods group. The Company produces and sells wine, cognac, perfumes, cosmetics, luggage, watches and jewelry.




Corporate Information
Address:

22 Avenue Montaigne
Paris, 75008
France


