LVMH Moët Hennessy Louis Vuitton Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 3:13 PM ET
Textiles, Apparel and Luxury Goods

Company Overview of LVMH Moët Hennessy Louis Vuitton Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
LVMH Moët Hennessy Louis Vuitton Inc. manufactures and markets luxury goods such as perfumes, jewelry, and leather goods. LVMH Moët Hennessy Louis Vuitton Inc. was incorporated in 1980 and is based in New York, New York. LVMH Moët Hennessy Louis Vuitton Inc. operates as a subsidiary of LVMH Moët Hennessy Louis Vuitton S.E.


19 East 57th StreetNew York, NY 10022United StatesFounded in 1980



Phone: 212-931-2000

Fax: 212-931-2903








Key Executives for LVMH Moët Hennessy Louis Vuitton Inc.




