      	Chairman and Chief Executive Officer
      








Mr. Bernard Arnault


      	Chairman of LVMH and Chief Executive Officer of LVMH
      


Age: 68
        







Mr. Louise Firestone


      	Senior Vice President and General Counsel
      








Mr. Nicolas Ghesquière


      	Artistic Director
      


Age: 45
        




Compensation as of Fiscal Year 2017. 

LVMH Moët Hennessy Louis Vuitton Inc. Key Developments

LVMH Inc. Appoints Anish Melwani as Chairman & CEO, Effective January 4, 2016
Oct 27 15
LVMH announced the appointment of Anish Melwani as Chairman & CEO of LVMH Inc., effective January 4, 2016. Anish will be based in New York, and be responsible for the development of LVMH activities in North America. Anish joins LVMH from McKinsey & Company, where he co-leads the Global Strategy & Corporate Finance practice and supports clients across industries.


